title: Tell Em Steve-Dave (TESD) - Vinylcast ll
description:
The second vinylcast from Tell 'Em Steve Dave. If you're here you know what this is already.

Uploaded for those that can't afford $35 plus shipping or who don't have a desire to own a physical album. They'll surely be constantly referencing this on the free pod for the next few weeks, maybe even months, and here's your free, easy and morally questionable way of knowing what they're talking about and actually being able to follow along
